race.description: Ladbrokes Blackbook Max 150 Points Heat 4 H
race.comment: ROLLING EXPRESS (1) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from four starts. Below best last time at Casino (17.40) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths fourth. Looks a leading chance on best. FEDERAL COSMIC (2) ran a nice race two back to fill a minor placing then got off the mark last time (20.34) at this track over 350m. Nicely drawn here. Yet to win here but has run some good races. Bold showing expected again. BOBBY BONUS (3) was checked in the run and safely held when seventh (21.16) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Expected to feature on best form. HURRICANE FREYA (8) can find the frame without surprising.
